BIOME.description: Checks if the biome that the user, target entity, or location is in is one of the listed biomes

BLOCK.description: Checks if the location has one of the listed blocks

CHANCE.description: A chance for this condition to be true

COOLDOWN.description: Checks if the time since the get last effect triggered is after the cooldown

DISTANCE.description: Checks if the distance between the user and target entity is in the range

ENTITY.description: Checks the target entity against this whitelist/blacklist

FLY.description: Checks if the user or target entity is flying

FLYING.description: Checks if the user or target entity is flying

HEALTH.description: Checks if the hp percentage of the user or target entity is in the range

HEIGHT.description: Checks if the user or target entity y coordinate is in the range

HOTBARSLOT.description: Checks if the held item/main hand in in a range of hotbar slots

INBLOCK.description: Checks if the user or target entity is in one of the listed blocks

ININVENTORY.description: Checks if the user have their inventory GUI opened

ITEM.description: Checks the item or the item in the declared slot against the declared item

ITEMWRAPPER.description:
Checks if all inside conditions are true. 
The item will be set as the item in the specified slot of the user or target entity

NPC.description: Checks if the user or target entity is an npc

ONGROUND.description: Checks if the user or target entity is on the ground

POTIONEFFECT.description: Checks whether the user or target entity has the potion effect

SHIELDED.description: Checks if the user is blocking

SHOOTER.description: Checks whether the shooter of the `OTHER` entity is the `SELF` entity

SIZE.description: Checks if the size of the user or target entity is in the range (for slimes, magma cubes, and phantoms)

SNEAK.description: Checks if the player or entity is shifting

SPEED.description: Checks whether the speed of the user or target entity is in the range

SPRINTING.description: Checks if the user or target entity is sprinting

SWIMMING.description: Checks if the user or target entity is swimming

TAMED.description: Checks if the target entity is tamed

TEMPERATURE.description: Checks if the location or the location of the user or target entity is in the range

TIME.description: Checks the relative in-game time (time of day) of the world that the player is in against the range. Measured in milli-hours or hours*1000

VISIBILITY.description: Checks if the user has a direct line of sight to the target entity

WEATHER.description: Checks if the world that the user is in has a storm

WORLD.description: Checks if the world that the user, target entity, or location is in is one of the listed worlds

WRAPPER.description: Checks if all inside conditions are true

ACTIONBAR.description: Sends an action bar to the user or target entity

AOE.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for every entity in the range. 
The target entity will be set to the entity this trigger triggers for

ARROW.description: Shoot an arrow to the location of the target entity

ATTRIBUTE.description: Modifies an attribute owned by the user or target entity

BLOCKENTITY.description: Change the block at target entity for a duration of time, then change it back. Same as WEB

BONEMEAL.description: Applies bonemeal to the location or location of the user or target entity

CANCEL.description: Cancels the event that triggered this effect

DAMAGE.description: Damages the user or the target entity

FIRE.description: Sets the user or target entity on fire. Same as FIRE

FLING.description: Modifies the velocity of the user or target entity. Same as FLING

FLY.description:
Sets the ability for the creative flight. Alias for FLYING 

Modes: 
SELF: For the user;
OTHER: For the target entity.

FLYING.description:
Sets the ability for the creative flight. Alias for FLYING 

Modes: 
SELF: For the user;
OTHER: For the target entity.

FREEZE.description: Modifies the user or target entity freezing ticks (ie. powdered snow effect)

GIVEITEM.description: Gives the user or target entity an item

GLIDING.description: Sets the gliding mode of the user or target entity (works even if an Elytra is not equipped)

HEALTH.description: Modifies the health of the user or target entity. Also rounds down to the nearest hitpoint/half a heart

HUNGER.description: Modifies the hunger value of the user or target entity

IGNITE.description: Sets the user or target entity on fire. Same as FIRE

ITEMMATERIAL.description: Changes the item type in a slot

ITEMSTACK.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the item in the slot. 
The item will be set to the item in the slot

KNOCKBACK.description: Applies a velocity to the target entity in the direction that the user is looking as the direction

LAUNCH.description:
Launches an entity. 
Mode `OTHER`: Launched in the direction of the target entity. 
Mode `SELF`: Launched in the direction the user is facing

LIGHTNING.description: Summons lightning on the user or target entity.

LOCATIONCUBE.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for every location in the cube around the user or target entity. 
The location will be set as the location the trigger triggers for

LOCATIONOFFSET.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers the location of the user or target entity after being offseted. 
The location will be set as the location the trigger triggers for

LOSETARGET.description: Make the user lose interest in the current target

LUNGE.description: Applies an acceleration to the user or the target entity based on the direction the entity is looking

MESSAGE.description: Sends a chat message to the user or target player

MODIFY.description: Modifies a variable, either user defined or not

NEAREST.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the nearest entity in the radius. 
The target entity will be set as the nearest entity

PICKUP.description: Pick up the target entity and places it on the user's head

PLACEBLOCK.description: Replaces a block at the location for an amount of time. Retains the original block data

POTION.description: Applies the potion effect to the user or target entity

PROJECTILE.description:
Shoots an entity from the user. 
Mode `SELF`: Shoots in the direction that the user is looking. 
Mode `OTHER`: Shoots at the target entity. 
Mode `LOCATION`: Shoots at the location

RANDOMTELEPORT.description: Teleports the user or target entity a random distance

RAYTRACE.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Sends out a raytrace that collides with entities or blocks in the direction that the user or target entity is looking. 
The target entity will be set as the collided entity. 
The location will be set as the location of the collided block

REMOVEENTITY.description: Removes the user or target entity

REMOVEPOTION.description: Removes potion effects from the user or target entity

RESIZE.description: Resizes the user or target entity (for slimes, magma cubes, and phantoms)

SCRAMBLEINVENTORY.description: Scrambles the inventory of the user or target entity

SHOOTER.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the target entity. 
The new target entity will be set as the source of the projectile if the old target entity is a projectile, otherwise the target entity will remain the same

SMITE.description: Summons lightning on the user or target entity.

SOUND.description: Plays a sound at the location or at the location of the user or target entity

SPAWNENTITY.description: Spawns an entity at the location or the location of the user or target entity

SWAP.description: Swaps the position of the user and target entity

SWITCHEROO.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
The target entity will be set as the original user.
 the user will be set as the original target entity

TARGET.description: If the user is a mob, sets the target of the user to the target entity

TELEPORT.description: Teleports the user to the location or the location of the target entity

TIMER.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for a number of times with a period and initial delay. 
Target items will be forwarded

VEINMINER.description: Breaks surrounding blocks around a location recursively

VELOCITY.description: Modifies the velocity of the user or target entity. Same as FLING

WAIT.description:
Acts like a trigger. 
Waits a duration of time before it triggers

WEB.description: Change the block at target entity for a duration of time, then change it back. Same as WEB

BECOMEVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when an entity enters the user, thus using the user as a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the entering entity

BLOCKBREAK.description:
Triggers when the user breaks a block. 
The location will be set as the location of the broken block

CHANGEMAINHAND.description:
Triggers when the user changes where the main hand slot is (i.e. scrolls or hits a number). 
The item will be set as the item in the new slot

COMBAT.description:
Triggers when the user damages an entity or gets damaged by an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity or the damaging entity respectively

CONSUME.description: Triggers when the user consumed an item

DAMAGEDBYENTITY.description:
Triggers when an entity damages the user. 
The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

DAMAGEDENTITY.description:
Triggers when the user damage an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity

DEATH.description:
Triggers when the user is killed. 
The target entity will be set as the killer if it exist

ENTERVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when the user enters a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the vehicle

EQUIPARMOR.description:
Triggers when the user equips an armour. 
The item will be set as the equiped item

EXITVEHICLE.description:
Triggers when the user exits a vehicle. 
The target entity will be set as the vehicle

INTERACTENTITY.description:
Triggers when the user right clicks an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the interacted entity

KILL.description:
Triggers when the user kills an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the killed entity

LAUNCHPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when the user launched a projectile. 
The target entity will be set as the launched projectile

MOVE.description:
Triggers when the user moves. 
The location will be set as the location the user moves to

PLAYERJOIN.description: Triggers when the user joins the server

PLAYERQUIT.description: Triggers when the user exits the server

PROJECTILEHIT.description:
Triggers when a projectile shot by the user landed and/or hits an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the projectile

RIPTIDE.description: Triggers when the user activates the riptide enchantment

SPRINT.description: Triggers when the user starts or stops sprinting

SWAPHANDS.description: Triggers when the user swaps hands

TAME.description:
Triggers when the user tames an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the tamed entity

TARGET.description:
Triggers when the user targets an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the target

TARGETED.description:
Triggers when the user is targeted by an entity. 
The target entity will be set as the entity that targeted the user

TOGGLEGLIDE.description: Triggers when the user glides or unglides

TOTEM.description:
Triggers when the user activates a totem. 
The target entity will be set as the killer of the user

DAMAGED.description: Triggers when the user gets damaged

DAMAGEDBYPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when an entity damages the user. 
If the damaging entity is a projectile, the target entity will be set as the source of the projectile. 
Otherwise, The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

DAMAGEDENTITYWITHPROJECTILE.description:
Triggers when the user damages an entity directly or with a projectile. 
The target entity will be set as the damaged entity

INTERACT.description: Triggers when the user interacts with a block or air

LOOP.description: Triggers periodically every couple of ticks

POTIONEFFECT.description: Triggers when a potion effect is applied to the user

PROJECTILECOMBAT.description: Acts like the DAMAGEDBYPROJECTILE and DAMAGEDENTITYWITHPROJECTILE triggers combined
